We need to show `(j+1) * 2^(j-1) ≥ 2^j`.
`2^j = 2 * 2^(j-1)`.
So we need to show `(j+1) * 2^(j-1) ≥ 2 * 2^(j-1)`.
This is true if `j+1 ≥ 2`, which is true for `j ≥ 1`.
So `(j+1).factorial ≥ 2^j`.

