  apply (div_le_div_iff (by positivity) (by positivity)).mpr
  nlinarith
exact_mod_cast h9
```

**Second part:** `n ^ k / (k.factorial : ℚ) ≤ n ^ k / 2 ^ (k - 1)`

This inequality simplifies to `1 / k! ≤ 1 / 2^(k-1)`, which is equivalent to `2^(k-1) ≤ k!`.

