  have h10 : (n ^ k : ℚ) > 0 := by positivity
  nlinarith [h8, h10]
linarith
```

We have proven `h7`. Now we can finish the proof of `h3`.

```tactics
have h8 : (n ^ k : ℚ) / (k.factorial : ℚ) ≤ (n ^ k : ℚ) / (2 ^ (k - 1) : ℚ) := by
  apply (div_le_div_iff (by positivity) (by positivity)).mpr
  linarith
linarith
```

So we have proven the second inequality: `↑n ^ k / ↑k.factorial ≤ ↑n ^ k / 2 ^ (k - 1)`.

The theorem `bound_binomial_coeff` is now proven.
